    "en": {
      "title": "Six people arrested for damaging SLPP MPs property",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); Police have arrested six suspects from Homagama and Weliwita, for causing damages to the house and property of MP Premanath C. Dolawatte, on the 9th of May.",
        "The suspects will be produced at the Kaduwela Magistrate's Court today (27).",
        "Police said that two suspects were arrested for attacking the Jeep of MP Sumith Udukumbura on the 10th of May.",
        "The suspects were arrested in the Daramitipola and Panliyadda areas and Police also seized a motorcycle used by the suspects to carry out the attack."
      ],
